p: \bI won't tell you my name, kid.
\bBut check out that cave. Something you've wanted for a very long time might happen.
\bYou guys... were chosen. By Arceus. To guard the... you know.
\bThe strongest trainers throughout all of history.
\bI'm such a huge fan, Steven, Cynthia. I-
\bReally, Cyn? This is the one you want to trust with the crystal? If Arceus finds-
\rHe's more strong-hearted than he seems, Steven.
\rI'm sure he'll make a worthy ally.
\rAdam. You know why you're here, right?
\bI... yes. All the cults... all the chaos in the region...
\bI can't stop it alone. I need your help.
\bAnd how, pray tell, did you learn about our group?
\bI was on Route 2, and I saw Cynthia in action-
\bShe was hidden! But I saw her Lucario Mega Evolve in order to protect a baby Riolu.
\bPokemon can't Mega Evolve on their own.\nI knew there was something fishy going on... and I found her hiding in a nearby cave.
\bShe wasn't going to say anything, but when she noticed I had Hoopa, she mentioned this... this whole thing.
\b...Cynthia. We've talked about this. You have to be more careful.
\rHoopa's chosen him, Steven! He's trustworthy! I know it!
\b... we put it to a vote.
\bUnfortunately, the side that was for you borrowing the crystal was nearly unanimous.
\bBut Adam, you need to listen carefully.
\bEven we don't know what the crystal is for... all we know is that Arceus wants it guarded.
\bAnd if Arceus wants it guarded, then it's clearly very important.
\bPeople have tried to steal it before, and you cannot let that happen.
\bThey're no threat! Not with that crystal by my side!
\bThey're not cultists. They're... something else. I'm not entirely sure.
\bFortunately, they can't just steal it from you. They'd need to defeat you first.
\bMy group has decided to lend you this crystal, against my counsel, to help you deal with the huge cult problems that Torren has.
\bBut you have to return it- you cannot let it fall into the hands of Giratina's group!
\bYou cannot lose to them. Do you understand?
\bI won't let you down, guys. I won't lose!
